org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules

Class MapTileAssetsProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules.MapTileModuleProviderBase
      • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules.MapTileFileStorageProviderBase
        • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules.MapTileAssetsProvider

  • public class MapTileAssetsProvider
extends MapTileFileStorageProviderBase
    Implements a file system cache and provides cached tiles from Assets. This functions as a tile provider by serving cached tiles for the supplied tile source. tiles should be put into apk's assets directory just like following example: assets/Mapnik/11/1316/806.png
